Package org.vladislavb.onemediatesttask.security

Record Class CustomUserDetails

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.vladislavb.onemediatesttask.security.CustomUserDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
public record CustomUserDetails(User user) extends Record implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
CustomUserDetails is a custom implementation of the Spring Security UserDetails interface. It wraps a User entity and provides Spring Security with user-specific data such as password, username, and account status. This class is used to authenticate and authorize the user within the Spring Security framework.
Author:
Vladislav Baryshev
